    <description>Migrated from the Opportunity Stage Update vs Quote Status process using multiple criteria.
Opportunity Stage is going through different phases based on how Quote Status is changed, RO-1300, RO - 1491, RO-1461, RO-1510, RO-1547, RO-1765, RO-2097</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>formula_PaymentTime</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
     ISBLANK({!$Record.dPaymentTime__c}),
     TODAY() + 14,
     TODAY()+{!$Record.dPaymentTime__c
})</expression>
    </formulas>
